```class Solution {
    public boolean canConstruct(String s, int k) {
        int[] count = new int[26];
        for (char c : s.toCharArray()) {
            count[c - 'a']++;
        }
        int oddCount = 0;
        for (int i : count) {
            i /= 2;
            if (i > 0) {
                oddCount++;
            }
            if (i > k / 2) {
                return false;
            }
        }
        return oddCount <= k;
    }
}```
